            expectations and drive sustainable transformation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h3 class="font-normal text-[1.7rem]">Vision</h3>
          <p>To be Kenya’s leading catalyst for people growth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start space-y-4 w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <h3 class="font-normal text-[1.7rem]">Our Values</h3>
        <p>
          <span class="font-semibold pr-4">Excellence:</span>We deliver with
          quality and precision.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="font-semibold pr-4">Integrity:</span>We act ethically and
          keep our word.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="font-semibold pr-4">Innovation:</span>We embrace learning
          and forward-thinking.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="font-semibold pr-4">Leadership:</span>We champion
          transformation at every level.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="font-semibold pr-4">Safety & Assurance:</span>We promote
          safe and thriving workplaces.
        </p>
        <p>
